title: The Flaming Lips - The Time Has Come to Shoot You Down... What a
description:
ARTIST: The Flaming Lips
ALBUM: The Time Has Come to Shoot You Down... What a Sound
FORMAT: MPEG Audio (MP3)
GENRE: Alternative

Track-by-track cover album of the Stone Roses' debut, featuring Peaking Lights, Stardeath and White Dwarfs, Spaceface and others. 

I know it's near impossible to buy this album, but do support the band by buying some of their other releases or merchandise if you like this
